title: GLiTRS
description: a set of effect sizes corresponding to the effect of anthropogenic activities on insects, published by Diversity and Distributions under the title “A multi-threat meta-analytic database for understanding insect biodiversity change”.
citation: Millard, J., Skinner, G., Bladon, A., Cooke, R., Outhwaite, C., Rodger, J. G., Barnes, L. A., Isip, J., Keum J., Raw, C., Wenban-Smith, E., Dicks, L. V., Hui, C., Jones, I. J., Woodcock, B., Isaac, N. J. B., 2025. Purvis, A. A multi-threat meta-analytic database for understanding insect biodiversity change. Diversity and Distributions
